title: RAK12016 WisBlock Flex Sensor Module > RAK12016 WisBlock Flex Sensor Module > Product Description > RAK12016 Flex Sensor Module Overview
content: RAK12016 is a flex sensor module, a part of the RAKWireless WisBlock Sensor series. It uses an FS-L-0095-103-ST from Spectrasymbol, which can measure the amount of deflection or bending.
parent_content: RAK12016 is a flex sensor module, a part of the RAKWireless WisBlock Sensor series. It uses an FS-L-0095-103-ST from Spectrasymbol, which can measure the amount of deflection or bending.

title: RAK12016 WisBlock Flex Sensor Module > RAK12016 WisBlock Flex Sensor Module > Prerequisites > Required Components for RAK12016 Setup
content:
To use a **RAK12016**, you need at least a **FS-L-0095-103-ST Flex Sensor** and **WisBlock Base** to plug the module in. **WisBlock Base** provides power supply to the **RAK12016** module. Furthermore, you need a **WisBlock Core** module to use the sensor.  
> **WARNING:** Make sure to fix the module with the screws to ensure a proper function.
